## 7. Index Annotations

```java
@Indexed                                       // single-field index
@Indexed(unique = true)                        // unique constraint
@Indexed(expireAfterSeconds = 86400)           // TTL — auto-delete after 24h
@TextIndexed                                   // full-text search
@TextIndexed(weight = 2)                       // higher relevance in text search

// Compound indexes — always at class level
@CompoundIndex(name = "status_date", def = "{'order_status':1,'created_at':-1}")

// Multiple compound indexes
@CompoundIndexes({
    @CompoundIndex(name = "status_date", def = "{'order_status':1,'created_at':-1}"),
    @CompoundIndex(name = "user_status", def = "{'user_id':1,'order_status':1}")
})
```

